=\"\" data-ratio=\"threeByTwo\" data-round=\"false\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tvline.com/news/amazon-more-ads-prime-video-commercials-increase-1235458538/\" title=\"\" target=\"_self\" data-card-index=\"1\" data-post-id=\"1235458538\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/reacher-prime-video.jpg?w=300\u0026amp;h=200\u0026amp;crop=1\" alt=\"Reacher Season 4 Preview Date\" height=\"200\" width=\"300\" loading=\"lazy\" data-attachment-id=\"1235452432\" data-wp-size=\"nova_size__threebytwo_small_cropped\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe third and final, 11-episode season of \u003ca href=\"https://tvline.com/t/prime-video/\" id=\"auto-tag_prime-video\" data-tag=\"prime-video\"\u003ePrime Video\u003c/a\u003e‘s YA series will premiere Wednesday, July 16. (A specific release pattern was not made immediately available, because that’d be too easy.)\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eA farewell poster (below) has also been released, and on Wednesday, the streamer unveiled a new trailer for the final episodes, which continues the show’s tradition of using Taylor Swift songs to illustrate the Conrad/Belly/Jeremiah love triangle. This time, it’s “Daylight” and “Red (Taylor’s Version).” You can watch it above.\n\n\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1024\" width=\"819\" src=\"https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/The-Summer-I-Turned-Pretty-Season-Three-Tease-Art.jpg?w=650\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/The-Summer-I-Turned-Pretty-Season-Three-Tease-Art.jpg 1080w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/The-Summer-I-Turned-Pretty-Season-Three-Tease-Art.jpg?resize=160,200 160w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/The-Summer-I-Turned-Pretty-Season-Three-Tease-Art.jpg?resize=240,300 240w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/